OL,3,CIslamophopia 'has increased' after
OL,4,CSouthport riots, survey finds
OL,6,FAlmost two-thirds, 62%, said the
OL,7,Fpotential risk of harm to Muslim
OL,8,Fcommunities had since increased.
OL,10,FWhile one in three Muslims surveyed
OL,11,Fsaid they had considered leaving the
OL,12,FUK as a result of the violence - which
OL,13,Fsaw mosques and hotels housing asylum
OL,14,Fseekers targeted - 55% said they felt
OL,15,Fsafe or very safe in the UK.
