OL,3,CIslamophopia 'has increased' after
OL,4,CSouthport riots, survey finds
OL,6,FIman Atta, Tell Mama director, said:
OL,7,F"Many British Muslims are very scared
OL,8,Fat the moment. They need our
OL,9,FGovernment to show it hears their
OL,10,Ffears, and is working to keep them
OL,11,Fsafe.
OL,13,F"More work must be done to reassure
OL,14,Fthese people. And we need greater
OL,15,Ffocus on supporting social cohesion in
OL,16,Fthe worst affected areas."
OL,18,FThe survey also showed that around
OL,19,Fhalf feel more able to be open about
OL,20,Ftheir identity.
