OL,3,CIslamophopia 'has increased' after
OL,4,CSouthport riots, survey finds
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "These
OL,7,Fresults are extremely concerning.
OL,8,FAttacks and hatred against Muslim
OL,9,Fcommunities are unacceptable and we
OL,10,Fhave been clear that we will seek to
OL,11,Fstamp out Islamophobia and racism
OL,12,Fwherever it occurs.
OL,14,F"All communities must feel safe,
OL,15,Fespecially in places of worship, which
OL,16,Fis why we introduced the Protective
OL,17,FSecurity for Mosques scheme and will
OL,18,Fcontinue to work with communities and
OL,19,Facross government to deliver a new
OL,20,Fapproach to tackling racial and
OL,21,Freligious hatred."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
