OL,3,CIslamophopia 'has increased' after
OL,4,CSouthport riots, survey finds
OL,6,FThe rioting that spread throughout the
OL,7,Fcountry was sparked by the stabbing of
OL,8,Fthree girls in Southport as they
OL,9,Fattended a dance class during the
OL,10,Fsummer holidays.
OL,12,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,13,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,14,Fseven, died following the attack at
OL,15,FThe Hart Space on a small business
OL,16,Fpark shortly before midday on 29 July.
OL,18,FThe night after the attack, disorder
OL,19,Fbroke out in the seaside town, by
OL,20,Fthose believed to be supporters of
OL,21,FEnglish Defence League.
